Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:36.00,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be1\an8}翻译：白い流星；特效：Noeru、Tiger Soldier；\N时间：eyre15gzc；后期：zipwinmax；繁化：黑羽侖人。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:10.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}さらば　昨日までの口づけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:14.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}さらば　いとおしき胸の痛みよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}まあ　それはそれとしてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:20.11,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}何とか今日も生きています
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}孤独とか過去とか噂とか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:30.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}欲望とか身内とかクセとか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}明日からおれらきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.62,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}もう笑われずにすみそうだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:41.53,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}“信じていればいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:44.51,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}気持ちはちゃんと伝わってくよ…”と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:50.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ふざけないでよ　だって　そうじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:55.61,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}もう　どこへも逃げたりしたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:59.48,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}誰が“yes！”といって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}だって　昨日の場所には戻れない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:07.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君といた場所には
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:11.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}もう　誰にも言い訳したくない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:16.01,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}だから“yes！”といって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:20.03,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}だって誰でもいーわけない　そうじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:24.47,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君じゃなきゃ意味がない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:29.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}こたえなんか　誰も知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:10.00,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}再见了  终结于昨日的亲吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:14.35,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}再见了  我那可怜的心伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.68,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}算了  不提也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:20.11,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今天也先想方设法活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.79,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}什么孤独  过去  和传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:30.88,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}什么欲望  全身  跟癖好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.15,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}从明天起  我一定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.62,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不用再强颜欢笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:41.53,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}“只要坚信这一点  总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:44.51,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}会将心情完全传达…”这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:50.33,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}别逗了啦  难道不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:55.61,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我也已经不想再逃到什么地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:59.48,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}虽然有人说“yes！”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.49,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}可还是无法回到昨日的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:07.71,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}那是和你一起度过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:11.68,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}已经不想向任何人辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:16.01,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}所以说“yes！”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:20.03,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}因为任何人都已不再辩解  不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:24.47,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不是你的话就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:29.59,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}答案什么的  谁都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  炼乳这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在家里做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连蛋黄酱都可以做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学真的很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  下次要我教你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好幸福～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外也教教百目鬼同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百目鬼他应该不会想学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  人多一点不是更有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家在那边  就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去路上小心一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:57.67,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,410)}秘  密{\fs16}\N\N{\fs18}伶 仃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本酒和下酒菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有很新鲜的比目鱼做的菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海鲜店的大叔说个个都生龙活虎的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才推荐我买下的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没伤到哪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日才是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就去收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是突然小拇指就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拇指就？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就开始疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:03:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小葵她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾了手指
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小葵勾过手指的那个小拇指发疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才弄掉了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它还有过什么类似的情况吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好月色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百目鬼…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是百目鬼的爷爷…对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…遥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了还来我们寺里有何贵干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么大事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静他睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫醒他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么特别的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没什么特别的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会这样来这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟静不好开口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟我说说看如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟遥先生您？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说确实是很要命的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那个有尸体的人家在井口取水的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会进到里面去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为包瓶子的布飘进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候突然小拇指疼了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和那个叫小葵的勾过手指的指头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵她可不是什么幸运女神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵她又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细回想一下的话  自从小葵她出现之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直发生不好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说不好的事情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是偶然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这个世界上没有什么偶然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…有的只是必然」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚听到这话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直觉得没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能所有事情都是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话  虽然只有一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但开始觉得确实会不会是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生的一切事情都有其意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能够全部都注意到的人却只是极其少数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在每天发生的全部事情中找出所有的意义」  这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光想想就让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能注意到这个事情是不是有什么意义的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「注意到」这个行为本身就有它的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为正是去思考「为什么」才会有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「注意到」这个行为是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边被各种各样的事情所引导着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有注意到的时光已经不会再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就由你来选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和静在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和百目鬼…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天请一定…知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在睡觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人有点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宝物库里有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说四月一日要去上学  所以可以先走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…早饭就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…说「绝对要做好」的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会好好做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连摩可拿那份也要做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有酒也要准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大清早就喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天梦里的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很想跟侑子小姐商量…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她说「帮我做早饭」所以我才住下的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果吃饭的时候竟然不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来都不考虑别人的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小羽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么早出门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想表示一下感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能陪我一起玩非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是玩得好高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:10:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头再一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天做了奶油蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我马上就要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…就拿着这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我送你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟和谁勾过手指了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爷爷他又出现在你梦里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的跟遥先生长得一模一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为长得太像了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得我老觉得是你在抽烟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉蛮怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实爷爷他年轻的时候是跟我长得一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话应该反过来说才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你跟你爷爷长得一模一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爷爷他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去世了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在我上小学5年级的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  为什么会是那么年轻的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  在那之前  为什么会在我的梦里冒出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许发生过什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅会帮人除灵和使用法术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也有做过「预知梦」那样的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很不可思议的一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥先生他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来在梦里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我说过「明天要和你在一起」这样的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的梦里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是和小葵的话倒还可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  奶油蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的路上遇到小羽  我送给她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天就没有点心吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你摆那张臭脸  没有就是没有了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个好吃鬼大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一直等我社团活动结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我问你为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为吃不到奶油蛋糕  才想让我去你家帮你做什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么那么自我主义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称百目鬼大人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就是四月一日大大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟和谁勾过手指了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉你脸色不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有勉强自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去教室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:14:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上  我遇到小羽了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个灵能师？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就因为我当时把奶油蛋糕送给小羽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百目鬼那家伙后来对我瞪了好久…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能以和现在的静同样年纪的样子出现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子无法渡越梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…如果我不是这个样子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计也没法拉住你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在呼唤你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快回去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从学校的2楼上掉下去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和窗户的玻璃一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好在下面看到的百目鬼他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想马上叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我用自己的使役传话  让他把你送到店里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刻不容缓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点就一切都晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在那边阻止了你对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在通往黄泉境界的梦里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐才将我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来应该会很贵吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…代价
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个的话  我已经收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那两个人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…你会在店里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她有进来的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了你一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:20:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有注意到的时光已经不会再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么说可能会惹你生气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想…一件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是没必要说的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  一直隐藏在心里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想就等于对小葵你撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从和小葵相识之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是有时…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了不好的事情是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是因为我锤了你的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果你那肩膀碰到的窗户玻璃就脱落了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也就那么摔了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:22:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…跟小葵你…是不是有什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于注意到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:15.93,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Lady　僕にみさしてくれよ　今日も君を夢に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:21.29,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Honey　僕に何度も何度も言わしてくれ　I'm lovin'
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.43,0:22:26.54,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そして全部受け止め　君のもとへ　虹の橋を架ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:31.28,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,また今夜も会えるといいな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:35.03,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がいると毎日が楽しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:37.64,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さらにさすがの僕も形無し
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:39.97,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仕事も遊びも勉強も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.67,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつもよりいっそEnjoyよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:44.91,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたは恋してますね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:48.20,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まじで？そうか　これは恋なのかって、まじで !!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:50.39,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真面目に君のすべて好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:53.26,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そこらのアイドル、モデルよりもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:56.04,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高くも低くもない君の背も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:22:58.73,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目も手も髪の匂いも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:01.32,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そして何以上に一緒いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:04.13,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他は何もいらないよ　一生涯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:11.31,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Lady　僕にみさしてくれよ　今日も君を夢に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:16.69,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Baby　私に何度も何度も言ってほしい　I'm lovin'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.92,0:23:21.94,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そして全部受け止め　君のもとへ　虹の橋を架ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:26.52,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,また今夜も会えるといいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.17,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いい男にはいい女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:32.80,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いい女にはいい男
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:35.46,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いい男にはいい女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.77,0:23:38.27,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いい女にはいい男
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:15.93,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Lady　注视着我　今天又一次梦见了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:21.29,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Honey　请对我说一次又一次　I'm lovin'
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.43,0:22:26.54,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受你的一切　将通向你的虹路架起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:31.28,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿今夜还能与你相会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:35.03,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在的每天充满欢声笑语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:37.64,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到你　就连我也忍俊不禁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:39.97,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论工作　玩乐还是学业
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.67,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因你的存在而喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:44.91,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱上了你哟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:48.20,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？这样啊　这就是恋爱　真的啦 !!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:50.39,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的喜欢上了全部的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:53.26,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些偶像模特都不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:56.04,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那不高不低的身材
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:22:58.73,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛　手指　还有头发的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:01.32,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和这一切永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:04.13,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无所求　此生只爱这唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:11.31,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Lady　注视着我　今天又一次梦见了你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:16.69,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Baby　我说了一次又一次　I'm lovin'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.92,0:23:21.94,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受你的一切　将通向你的虹路架起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:26.52,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿今夜还能与你相会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.17,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的我遇上最好的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:32.80,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的我爱上最好的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:35.46,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的我遇上最好的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.77,0:23:38.27,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的我爱上最好的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想你什么时候会来跟我这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是过了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来真的很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小葵你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.83,0:24:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百目鬼君和小葵都为了实现愿望而成了店里的客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我的伤势而付出了代价的人是…
